  * Update upstream URL in debian/copyright.
  * Bump Standards-Version to 3.7.3 (no changes).
  * Drop the XS- prefix from Vcs-Git and Vcs-Browser fields in debian/control.
  * Install the upstream ChangeLog.

  [ Julien Cristau ]
